                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=kaiuwe",
                        "name": "kaiuwe",
                        "displayName": "Kai Uwe",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "You can use not only the messageId for plural, because Zend_Translate and Gettext from PHP doesn't support it.\r\n\r\n* [Zend_Translate: Plural notations for Translation|http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/manual\/en\/zend.translate.plurals.html]\r\n* [PHP: ngettext|http:\/\/de3.php.net\/manual\/de\/function.ngettext.php]\r\n\r\n*Think out loud:* The both methods Zend_Navigation_Page::setLabel() and Zend_Form_Element::setLabel() accept an array like Zend_Translate_Adapter::translate()?",
